# The Conglomerate - Architecture

Single Cloudflare Worker app. React+Vite SPA + Hono API + D1 + R2, one deploy.

## Layout
- `src/client/` React app (routes, components, design tokens, lib).
  - `routes/` — thin page loaders; heavy UI belongs in `components/`.
  - `components/event/` — event detail, form, sidebar editors, tab panels.
  - `lib/` — `api.ts` envelope helper + domain clients and hooks.
    - Domain clients: `events`, `annotations`, `media`, `people`, `places`, `acts`, `admin`
    - Hooks: `useAsync`, `useDebouncedValue`, `useFilterOptions`, `useMediaQuery`
- `src/server/` Worker+Hono (routes, middleware, db, media, audit, lib, auth).
  - `db/queries/` — read queries by domain; barrel at `db/queries/index.ts`.
    - `events/` — `headliner.ts`, `list.ts`, `detail.ts` (barrel `events/index.ts`)
    - Also: `media`, `annotations`, `people` (includes places + act names), `admin`, `helpers`
  - `db/mutations/` — writes + audit; one file per domain:
    `events`, `people`, `places`, `media`, `annotations`, `uploads`
- `src/shared/` types + Zod schemas + DTOs reused by client and server.
- `migrations/` Drizzle-generated SQL. `scripts/` seed, export, PWA icon generation. `tests/` Vitest.
- `src/client/public/` static assets (PWA icons, favicon). Built SPA + PWA artifacts land in `dist/client/`.

## Request routing
The Worker (`src/server/index.ts`) runs first and owns `/api/*` and `/media/*`;
everything else is delegated to the `ASSETS` binding (SPA fallback). Never add
CORS - client and API share an origin.

## PWA (installable client)
- `vite-plugin-pwa` in `vite.config.ts` — manifest + Workbox service worker at build.
- `main.tsx` registers via `virtual:pwa-register` (`registerType: autoUpdate`, `injectRegister: null`).
- Build outputs: `dist/client/manifest.webmanifest`, `sw.js`, `workbox-*.js` (served by ASSETS).
- Precaches SPA shell (JS/CSS/fonts/icons). `/api` and `/media` are `NetworkOnly` — never cache archive data.
- Icons: static PNGs in `src/client/public/ico/` (favicons, PWA, apple-touch).
- Dev SW enabled (`devOptions.enabled`); artifacts go to `src/client/dev-dist/` (gitignored).

## Golden rules
- Shared enums live in `src/shared/types.ts`; DTOs in `src/shared/dto.ts` — import, never re-declare.
- Add config (limits, MIME lists, Access settings) to `src/server/lib/config.ts`,
  never hard-code inline.
- Client: domain API calls go in `src/client/lib/<domain>.ts`, not inline in routes/components.
- Server reads: `src/server/db/queries/<domain>.ts` (or `queries/events/`); import from `db/queries`.
- Server writes: `src/server/db/mutations/<domain>.ts` — routes never embed Drizzle writes.
- After changing `wrangler.toml`, run `npm run types`.
- Every milestone ends with `npm test` green and a working `wrangler dev`.
